Follow these simple steps to build VHPOP:

  ./configure [options]
  make

For brief information on how to run VHPOP, use the following command:

  ./vhpop --help

VHPOP has been successfully built on the following systems:

  Digital UNIX 4.0
  RedHat Linux 5.2, 6.2, 7.1, 8.0
  IRIX 6.5
  SunOS 5.7, 5.9

If you are unable to build VHPOP, please report your problems to
<lorens@cs.cmu.edu>.
